summary: “Embrace the void and have the courage to exist”. These 9 words means so much to me.  I wouldn’t be where I am today if it...
caption:
“Embrace the void and have the courage to exist”.
These 9 words means so much to me. 
I wouldn’t be where I am today if it wasn’t for Dan & Phil.. I’m not even sure I would be alive. 

I mostly just wanted to thank you @danielhowell for everything. Hopefully one day I get to meet you and have you write this down on a piece of paper so I can get it tattooed on my arm, because that’s something I’ve always wanted to do ever since I saw the video “ Existential Crisis “. 
I’m so grateful for you existing and I’m so happy you are in my life and that you make me feel loved. 

Thank you for everything.
Take care of each other and remember, Have the courage to exist.

xx
